OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and warm through much of
OL,6,Fthe day. Variable cloud and some
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells in the morning.
OL,8,FSunshine turning hazier in the
OL,9,Fafternoon as cloud spreads east.
OL,10,FChance of the odd shower in the late
OL,11,Fafternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe odd light shower possible
OL,14,Fat first, otherwise dry through the
OL,15,Fevening and overnight. Quite cloudy at
OL,16,Ffirst in the evening, some clearer
OL,17,Fspells may develop overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
