OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FDry with some bright or
OL,6,Fsunny spells in the morning. Turning
OL,7,Fcloudier through the day with the
OL,8,Fchance of some rain through the
OL,9,Fafternoon and evening. Warm again in
OL,10,Fsunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA
OL,13,Fchangeable period but often dry and
OL,14,Fbright with sunny spells. Some patchy
OL,15,Frain or a few showers possible at
OL,16,Ftimes, mainly in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
